Prometheus Docker
» docker run -d -p 9090:9090 -v <path-to-prometheus.yml>:/etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml prom/prometheus

example 
Update the target ip address and port in yml files
» docker run -d -p 9090:9090 -v /media/akshith/Others2/ISoSySc/MasterThesis/NewDocs_November/Code/SpringBoot/prometheus.yml:/etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml prom/prometheus

you can find the dashbaord at http://localhost:9090

Zipkin docker
» docker run -d -p 9411:9411 openzipkin/zipkin

you can find dashboard at http://localhost:9411/zipkin


Grafana

» docker run -d -p 3000:3000 grafana/grafana

you can find the dashboard at http://localhost:3000


To generate jar files

» mvn install 

To run 

» java -jar «Jar file name»


http://localhost:8080/portal-service/fullDetails/97

